H fluid. We find that the projected fluid\ncouples non-minimally to geometric deformations, indicating the presence of\ninternal geometric degrees of freedom.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Nov 2018 19:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2019 15:28:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-18"}
