lds, and of a far reaching generalization of Shidlovsky's lemma built upon\nthe approach of Bertrand-Beukers and Bertrand.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2018 14:39:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-22"}
